data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom 2019 built home  in the heart of Otsego!  The main level boasts luxury vinyl plank floors throughout seamlessly tying together all of the living space. The chefs-like kitchen includes custom Cosentino quartz countertops, matching S.S appliances, custom lighting, & a large island with extra seating. The inviting main level living room includes a cozy gas burning fireplace, recessed lighting, & great views of the backyard. The serene owners suite boasts a vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet, private 3/4 bathroom with tile floors, double sink vanity, & a walk in shower. Venture downstairs to find the recently finished lower level that includes luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, large wet bar with Cosentino quartz countertops, spacious living room, thoughtfully built-in kennel, large bedroom, & a 3/4 bathroom with the custom quartz countertops. Located just minutes away from multiple parks, restaurants, & shopping spots.
